name: Edward J. BARTA v. Sanford GORODETSKY et al.

parties: Edward J. BARTA v. Sanford GORODETSKY et al.

opinions.text:
ORDER
The plaintiff’s motion to dismiss is denied. Plaintiff’s petition for reconsideration and motion for injunctive relief are denied.
DORIS, J., did not participate.

attorneys: Keven A. McKenna, Providence, for plaintiff.
Vincent J. Piccirilli, Providence, for defendants.
casebody.head_matter:
Edward J. BARTA v. Sanford GORODETSKY et al.
No. 80-226-A.
Supreme Court of Rhode Island.
July 28, 1980.
Keven A. McKenna, Providence, for plaintiff.
Vincent J. Piccirilli, Providence, for defendants.
